rows.label: qst202606_msg0003
rows.name:
As Queen Lagert's information
stated, it seems there was a massive
outbreak here in Temperantia.

rows.label: qst202606_msg0004
rows.name: This number is a bit daunting...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202606_msg0005
rows.name:
But if we leave them, other
countries will suffer. We
can't just ignore this.

rows.label: qst202606_msg0006
rows.name:
You're right. We have to do
something to defeat them here.

rows.label: qst202606_msg0007
rows.name:
If it's decided...[ML:Dash ] let's
go! Ten'i, we're counting
on you this time too!
